<br>
What would its government sctructure look like? and the distribution of power?<br>
<br>
If there is any form of currency how will that NOT alter the balance of equality and power?<br>
<br>
I just don't see how socialism in this current age could work.  I am seriously trying to think outside of the capitalism box that I have lived my whole life in, so if you have any insight that will help me see what some of the socialists see please let me know.  I'm not looking to convert or anything, just to understand.<br>
